blog.description:
The Video Game Art Archive is dedicated to scanning and extracting classic video game artwork at the best resolutions possible!

Support us on Patreon!
We update four times a day with new artwork from long forgotten games that have never had their art available. Looking for a specific game? Check out the Archive! You might get lucky!

summary: NPD: The Nintendo Switch "Reached The Highest Year-To-Date Dollar Sales For Nintendo-Produced Hardware Since 2011"
title: NPD: The Nintendo Switch "Reached The Highest Year-To-Date Dollar Sales For Nintendo-Produced Hardware Since 2011"
body:
NPD: The Nintendo Switch “Reached The Highest Year-To-Date Dollar Sales For Nintendo-Produced Hardware Since 2011”

Nintendo‘s software had a quiet month, but it was anything but quiet for Nintendo’s hardware. The NPDGroup latest data, which has just been released, confirmed that the Nintendo Switch had yet another very successful month. According to NPD analyst Mat Piscatella, “Nintendo Switch is the best-selling hardware platform of February. And [for] 2019 year to date”. One reason for this is that, in…

The latest NPD data has been released. This information is for the month of February 2019. In the world of software, it was a relatively quiet month for Nintendo. The company didn’t release much. This, combined with the release of multiple major titles by other companies, means that there wasn’t anything noteworthy that the NPD Group could share about Nintendo software.
